    "lyrics": {
      "text": "By con-ceiv----ing the Wis--------dom_______ and_______ Word_____ of___ and__ Word of God in thy womb,____ with-out be--------ing_______ con-------sumed_____ there---con--sumed there-by, thou bar-------est___ for all_____ the___ world Him Who fill-----eth__ the____ u-------ni------𝂴---the__ u-ni-verse; thou hast held___ in___ thine arms______ Him that hold-----eth__ to----geth-------er______ 𝂴___ to--geth-er all, Who hath fash---ioned___ cre-a------tion and giv-----eth their____ food_______ to______ 𝂵___ their__ food to all. Where----fore,__ I___ be-seech-------thee, O thou all---ho---ly vir----gin and Moth----er__ of__ God,_____ that I____ be re---deemed____ from my man----y___ sins__ when I shall have___ to___ stand__ be----fore the Face of my__ Cre-a---tor__ and______ God; O pure La----dy___ Vir--------------gin,__ help____ me___ in__ that____ hour, for thou canst do___ what---so-ev-er thou_________ dost______ will,__ O__ all-----hymned____ 𝂴____ One."
